  }
}
```

### `mementor commits [--branch <name>]`

```json
{
  "commits": [
    {
      "hash": "c04a441f8e2b",
      "short_hash": "c04a441",
      "subject": "redesign schema from 4-table to 11-table architecture (#38)",
      "author": "heejoon.kang",
